{"id": 1802, "genre": 1001, "title": "出于对“效率”的痴迷，你都做过哪些事情？", "description": "上班摸鱼可以，这些时间，我一秒都不想浪费。", "record_count": 2941, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201707141206408IDyaWVAEKYFuTXZ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-07-17T03:00:05Z", "options": [{"id": 222464, "content": "列出一大堆的计划，然后一个也不执行", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081143}, {"id": 222465, "content": "为了效率，我坚持不熬夜工作，却熬夜玩了手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 667578}, {"id": 222721, "content": "一分钟没有学进去就浑身不适，稍微有点空闲就闭目养神，以便学习时更有精力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081964}, {"id": 222467, "content": "专心做一件事，效率最高。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041105}, {"id": 222723, "content": "各种日程app", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078317}, {"id": 223494, "content": "为了让我少动脑子，做什么事情我都会先到一个最快捷的方法", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1078712}, {"id": 222471, "content": "充分利用ddl第一生产力", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1054538}, {"id": 224011, "content": "不愿看望亲人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 829230}, {"id": 222733, "content": "手帐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1076757}, {"id": 222478, "content": "下载过无数提高效率的软件，至今到书店看到教你提高效率的书都有买的冲动", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 918627}, {"id": 222480, "content": "边刷牙边压腿\n边洗澡边深蹲\n边睡觉边提臀", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1050806}, {"id": 222481, "content": "网购", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950981}, {"id": 222484, "content": "边听文化访谈类节目边做PPT回复邮件和同事聊天", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746201}, {"id": 222486, "content": "一边看剧一边网购", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081243}, {"id": 222487, "content": "罚抄写课文用两支笔一起写", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 811981}, {"id": 222488, "content": "万事具备 只等死线", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034310}, {"id": 222490, "content": "WiFi太慢会毫不犹豫的换成4G", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081269}, {"id": 222491, "content": "想听或者看我想要表达感受的歌或者书，结果是没有一首或一本。等没有写来的快，问题是自己拖延不愿意写", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038300}, {"id": 222492, "content": "将时间安排的很紧凑，一秒钟都不浪费。去打一趟水，会顺便倒个垃圾，再上阳台收个衣服，同时打水的桶还在打水。(指在学校宿舍)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 841839}, {"id": 222748, "content": "每天都记录自己的起居餐饮工作内容健身安排，基本回忆和记录都要花半个小时，而且还要写日记练习文笔，想到这件事要花这么长时间，其他的任何事情都不敢耽搁，但做具体的事情时刚进入可持续的紧缩状态所安排的时间就已经到了，因此要极力让自己静下来，集中心力进入状态。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1082035}, {"id": 222749, "content": "坐地铁一定要带上一个本本画速写，哪怕只有半分钟，动了笔也是好的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1082035}, {"id": 222494, "content": "怎么省事怎么来，简单粗暴直达目标，不择手段", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1048616}, {"id": 222750, "content": "为了高效率，不停寻找方法", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1082049}, {"id": 231710, "content": "浪费时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1114972}, {"id": 222496, "content": "关机", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 758641}, {"id": 222497, "content": "边刷牙边上厕所哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855200}, {"id": 222753, "content": "只要能用钱解决的事，绝不花时间", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920921}, {"id": 222499, "content": "出门前会先开门观察电梯的位置，低于一半楼层则先穿外套鞋袜再出门。反之则先按键后再拿着鞋袜外套锁好门站在走廊穿。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079438}, {"id": 222500, "content": "为了整合心仪的素材可以耐着性子在那里搜索一整天", "image": "img/option/option/20170718091158tQbP4FgNkKxOW5Bv.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 331384}, {"id": 225828, "content": "看AV打飞机写作业喝水同时进行", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 932725}, {"id": 222502, "content": "做不需要用脑的工作时一定要放点什么看", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081353}, {"id": 222503, "content": "想好在家要做什么事情\n在家走动时 不走回头路 走一遍全部解决", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081357}, {"id": 222506, "content": "毫无效率", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081367}, {"id": 222509, "content": "学习快速阅读法，用手指来提高阅读速度", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041410}, {"id": 222765, "content": "没时间了，然后飞速干一件事", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1064923}, {"id": 222511, "content": "克扣睡觉时间看动漫", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1069166}, {"id": 224815, "content": "周五做完下周一的事免得周日过于悲伤", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 852189}, {"id": 227119, "content": "准时下班", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 75333}, {"id": 222512, "content": "网速太慢会毫不犹豫地换成4G", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1059247}, {"id": 222513, "content": "在超市排队结帐，队伍长时也把手机拿出来，看会儿书。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 939273}, {"id": 222769, "content": "卸载游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 437312}, {"id": 222514, "content": "把一些可以在吃饭走路坐车时解决的问题都安排得非常妥当后来发觉吃饭时看资料居然有更多意外的发现", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1081385}, {"id": 223030, "content": "做家务时 让app给我念书", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1015624}, {"id": 223038, "content": "不和别人废话，不和别人娱乐，边看书边听书，计划好每一秒的时间安排", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 271539}, {"id": 224069, "content": "强迫症的自己一定不会留下自己不常用的软件", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1084243}, {"id": 223561, "content": "在做事前关闭手机，泡一杯茶。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 997664}, {"id": 227658, "content": "只租走路到公司10分钟的房子，换工作一定换房子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 95936}, {"id": 224847, "content": "定了一大堆计划\n写了一本时间表\n买了几次小闹钟", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1073440}, {"id": 223824, "content": "同一个控件的使用方法，去年12月份一版，今年五月份一版，七月份又一版本", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1083570}, {"id": 222801, "content": "节约时间，放弃了自己做饭", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1082246}]}